Jellicent (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0592: Frillish
Pokémon
#0594: Alomomola →

Jellicent has been featured on 7 different cards since it debuted in the Noble Victories expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Jellicent cards are normally Water-type or Psychic-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Jellicent

Jellicent
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
